          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>WORLD-CLASS CRAFTSMANSHIP</strong> - timeless seasonal pieces designed, developed and executed by the world's best and most celebrated contributors to style and fashion</p><p></p><p><strong>REFINED MATERIAL</strong>- sourced from across the globe, our pieces and collections are anchored by a commitment to adopting the finest and most desired materials of our time</p><p></p><p><strong>TIMELESS ELEGANCE - </strong>the styling and execution across collections stand as our commitment to sophistication, embodying the attention to detail of iconic pieces of history</p>",
